{"tid":2058724,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【眾籌要人】中學生又比教育局搞，成年人可唔可以比D支持佢地？","createTime":"2020-06-10T11:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T12:45:44.000Z","uid":27797,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a86f0ab930f3f0d9df70026a5a58bec136f9ef76","tid":2058724,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:33:18.000Z","msg":"今日楊潤雄出信比哂校長，對班中學生話搞公投罷課要打要殺咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實除左罷課之外，之前單歷史科DSE試題，都有中學生企出黎要JR政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而政府為左對付班中學雞，出到最勁既大狀去打呢單官司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一句講哂，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>眾籌要人呀！</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌覆核考試局取消歷史試題 共抗政府DQ歷史試題 】<br />\n#守護思想自由 #捍衛教育自主<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">🗳眾籌連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/JR_DSEhist\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FJR_DSEhist&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=d12ddde8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/JR_DSEhist</a></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n早前，教育局施壓考評局要求取消有關試題。為反抗中共及政權對學生和教育界的打壓，<span style=\"color: red;\">中學生行動籌備平台在 2/6 正式向高等法院提交司法覆核申請，覆核考評局刪除試題的決定。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">司法覆核所需費用甚多，而敗訴後更需負擔對方的訟費及律師費。因考評局委聘了霍金路偉律師行（Hogan Lovells）、杜淦堃資深大律師、唐思佩大律師等「鑽石陣容」迎戰，而教育局亦有可能參與訴訟，律師團隊估算法律費用會很龐大，對方的法律費用將會超過100萬。</span><br />\n<br />\n為了保障申請人的訟費風險，我們必需籌募一定金額，令願意承擔法律風險的考生在敗訴後，不至於面對龐大債務。<br />\n<br />\n在與律師團隊商議後，<span style=\"color: red;\">我們期望是次眾籌能籌得120萬港元，並將所有款項用於是次司法覆核官司上，若有餘額則會捐贈予612人道救援基金。</span>法庭已正式排期在7月2-3日展開聆訊，因此我們希望在聆訊前籌得以上款項，讓申請人以及法律團隊免受過大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n教育塑造年輕人靈魂和意志，要避免城市沉淪，必先捍衛教育自主，從而才能培育出學生的品格和獨立思考。我們期望大眾能與一眾學子攜手，共同對抗中共對教育界的極權入侵。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n:iphone:TG subscibe 更多中學生罷課及行動資訊發佈undefinedoint_down:<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/SSStrike2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FSSStrike2019&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=8d326467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/SSStrike2019</a>"},{"pid":"6cc69b749b96f0ec29e992579795b2964e927547","tid":2058724,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:33:55.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713aa6c8be5066575c287e3a3eab8cfb5d4ec590","tid":2058724,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:34:12.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe899f63ec9c380d466f755ac45adab5f46fe32e","tid":2058724,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:34:34.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2fe20e56ffecd43142a4943865d06cedea9123","tid":2058724,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:35:04.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4192db584f6d80996ec21ccd5a1bc6e94ea766e7","tid":2058724,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:35:10.000Z","msg":"制道內投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5eb5c6420a1d222dcfe836a577fd79b4b292b8b","tid":2058724,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:36:03.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf15ba1bd45f6e6177b1dd7ae65cc9dceee0bbc2","tid":2058724,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb1f3a570db3168cbaa650bb71ca13a361983c8","tid":2058724,"uid":342909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"已捐 G持吿佢甩褲！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1a2140aeb6eb8867375159c73ad8b06ae0e8de","tid":2058724,"uid":333470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"543a7866b553f3494a5c0692a712bf6d9c0f8233","tid":2058724,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:06:08.000Z","msg":"中學生已成condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2cdd25f35e199249d54b89e730adb2d1ddac7e","tid":2058724,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"543a7866b553f3494a5c0692a712bf6d9c0f8233","tid":2058724,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:06:08.000Z","msg":"中學生已成condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:45:44.000Z","msg":"冇錯"}]}